data.description: Three bedroom, two bathroom, two car garage home in a nice established neighborhood; Living room features wood picture frame paneling & a brick wood burning fireplace, also has a sliding glass door that gives access to the peaceful backyard with covered patio; Built-in cabinets in foyer & two built-in corner desks in secondary bedrooms, one bedroom has a wall of built-in cabinets that would make a great crafting room; Large kitchen with electric five burner ceramic cooktop, wall oven, microwave & dishwasher; Kitchen, utility room, dining & foyer have ceramic tile flooring; Master bedroom has ensuite with separate dressing area, tile shower, & two walk-in closets; Hall bath features a tub-shower combination with tile surround, vanity & toilet; Window coverings, lighted ceiling fans, & tubular skylights throughout; Large backyard, wood privacy fence with concrete curbing; Sprinkler system in front & back; Storage building in backyard with electricity; Call to schedule a showing today!!
